        <h4><span class="x-icon">X</span> No Google Business Profile</h4>
        <p>You don't appear in Google Maps at all. When someone searches "handyman near me" in Boca Raton, you're invisible. Your competitors have 49-286 reviews and dominate the map pack. The map pack gets <strong>40%+ of all clicks</strong> for local service searches.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="check-item">
        <h4><span class="x-icon">X</span> No service-specific pages</h4>
        <p>You have one generic "handyman-services" page. You need individual pages for plumbing repairs, electrical work, drywall, kitchen remodeling, bathroom repairs, and more. Each page = a new chance to rank. Combined, these service keywords represent <strong>3,000+ monthly searches</strong>.</p>
        <div class="volume-tags">
