      <div class="check-item">
        <h4><span class="x-icon">X</span> No location pages</h4>
        <p>You serve Boca Raton, Delray Beach, and surrounding areas, but have zero location-specific pages. These are free traffic opportunities with zero keyword difficulty.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="check-item">
        <h4><span class="x-icon">X</span> Zero reviews anywhere</h4>
        <p>No Google reviews, no Yelp reviews, no BBB listing, no Angi profile. Reviews are the #1 trust signal for local service businesses. Your competitors have <strong>49-286 reviews</strong>.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="check-item">
        <h4><span class="x-icon">X</span> No blog or content</h4>
        <p>No blog means no long-tail keyword coverage, no topical authority, and no reason for Google to crawl your site regularly. Your 6 pages can only rank for a handful of terms.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="check-item amber-border">
        <h4><span class="x-icon amber">!</span> Missing meta descriptions & duplicate H1</h4>
        <p>Your About and Contact pages have no meta descriptions. Your contact page has a duplicate H1 tag. These are easy fixes that affect click-through rates from search results.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

